name:                bcbs-crawl
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            This repository contains the source code for a Haskell programm BcbsCrawler that searches the web site of the BCBS (Basel Committee for Banking Supervision) at www.bis.org/bcbs for any type of publication. The program then saves the accompanying pdf files and further information about the publications.
